OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775146264
OL,3,CEx-officer jailed for sexual assault
OL,4,Cand abusing trust after targeting two
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FAn ex-police officer who abused his
OL,8,Fposition and sexually assaulted a
OL,9,Fwoman while serving in the force has
OL,10,Fbeen jailed.
OL,12,FFormer Detective Constable Patrick
OL,13,FBanks befriended two women separately,
OL,14,Fsent them inappropriate messages,
OL,15,Fvisited their homes and, in one
OL,16,Fscenario, asked one of them to
OL,17,Ftranslate a message which read, "I
OL,18,Fwant to take off your underwear with
OL,19,Fmy teeth".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
