FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775146264
OL,3,CEx-officer jailed for sexual assault
OL,4,Cand abusing trust after targeting two
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FBanks, 42, who had served in Leeds
OL,8,Fwith West Yorkshire Police, was
OL,9,Freported by one of the women in April
OL,10,Flast year and arrested, before being
OL,11,Fsuspended from duty. The second woman
OL,12,Fcame forward to report him following
OL,13,Fhis arrest.
OL,15,FSheffield Crown Court heard on
OL,16,FWednesday that Banks met the women in
OL,17,F2024 and 2025, visiting his first
OL,18,Fvictim's home multiple times while off-
OL,19,Fduty and sexually assaulting her by
OL,20,Ftouching her inappropriately.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775146264
OL,3,CEx-officer jailed for sexual assault
OL,4,Cand abusing trust after targeting two
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FHe also regularly messaged his second
OL,8,Fvictim, visiting her four times at her
OL,9,Fhome with three of these visits being
OL,10,Foff-duty.
OL,12,FBanks was jailed for three years on
OL,13,FWednesday and given a seven-year
OL,14,Frestraining order. He was also made to
OL,15,Fsign the sex offenders register for
OL,16,Flife.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
