OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775146264
OL,3,CEx-officer jailed for sexual assault
OL,4,Cand abusing trust after targeting two
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FJudge Jeremy Richardson KC told Banks
OL,8,Fhe had "betrayed every ounce of trust"
OL,9,Finvested in him, and that any officer
OL,10,Fcommitting similar crimes should
OL,11,Fexpect to be punished.
OL,13,FSpeaking in court, one of the women
OL,14,Fsaid: "What revolts me is the man who
OL,15,Fwas supposed to help us took advantage
OL,16,Fof our vulnerability," adding what
OL,17,Fhappened had "destroyed" her trust for
OL,18,Fanyone in authority.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
