PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775146264
OL,3,CEx-officer jailed for sexual assault
OL,4,Cand abusing trust after targeting two
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FHis sentencing comes as ITV Calendar
OL,8,Freveals there have been 47 referrals
OL,9,Fto the Independent Office for Police
OL,10,FConduct from five of the region's
OL,11,Fforces since 2021 regarding abuse of
OL,12,Fpower for a sexual purpose.
OL,14,FAcross the country there were nearly
OL,15,Ffive hundred cases - approximately 100
OL,16,Fa year.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
