PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775146264
OL,3,CEx-officer jailed for sexual assault
OL,4,Cand abusing trust after targeting two
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FOne woman who was targeted by a
OL,8,Fserving officer at Humberside Police
OL,9,Fafter escaping an abusive relationship
OL,10,Fsaid the crime had "ruined any trust
OL,11,FI've got with any police".
OL,13,FEx-officer Simon Miller had collected
OL,14,FShannon Mulhall from a women's refuge
OL,15,Fwhen he had sex with her. He was
OL,16,Fcharged with misconduct in public
OL,17,Foffice and jailed in November 2023 for
OL,18,Ftwo years and four months.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
