PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775146264
OL,3,CEx-officer jailed for sexual assault
OL,4,Cand abusing trust after targeting two
OL,5,Cwomen
OL,7,FShannon Mulhall said: "I am still
OL,8,Fliving with nightmares; I am still
OL,9,Fliving with panic attacks. I am scared
OL,10,Fof leaving home in case I bump into
OL,11,Fhim. He could be anywhere."
OL,13,FBanks, who pleaded guilty to sexual
OL,14,Fassault and two counts of misconduct
OL,15,Fin public office, resigned from the
OL,16,Fforce following his arrest.
OL,18,FA misconduct panel in October ruled he
OL,19,Fwould have been dismissed had he still
OL,20,Fbeen serving.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
